{
  "id": "69a9aedf965e93a61b791a21",
  "title": "直接的な日本語ローマ字翻字案",
  "created": 1772728033,
  "updated": 1772729022,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a9aedf965e93a61b791a21",
      "text": "直接的な日本語ローマ字翻字案",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7b6",
      "text": "#ローマ字 #翻字",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728074
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7b9",
      "text": "`̈`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7ba",
      "text": "`̊`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b1850000000000edf7f7",
      "text": "`̱`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728709,
      "updated": 1772728713
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7bc",
      "text": "table:対照表",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7bd",
      "text": " \tあ\tか\tさ\tた\tな\tは\tま\tや\tら\tわ\tん",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7be",
      "text": " [訓令式]\ta\tk\ts\tt\tn\th\tm\ty\tr\tw\tn / nn",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7bf",
      "text": " 直接方式\t\tc/k̈\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tñ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c0",
      "text": " \t\tが\tざ\tだ\t\tば\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c1",
      "text": " 訓令式\t\tg\tz\td\t\tb\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c2",
      "text": " 直接方式\t\tg/k̈\ts̈\tẗ\t\tḧ\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c3",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\tぱ\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c4",
      "text": " 訓令式\t\t\t\t\t\tp\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c5",
      "text": " 直接方式\t\t\t\t\t\th̊\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9afb50000000000edf7e7",
      "text": "\tか行の子音について",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728245,
      "updated": 1772728411
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b04a0000000000edf7e8",
      "text": " \tCの派生文字がGである。というのも、オリジナルのローマ字（ラテン語アルファベット）ではcは常にkの音価で発音されるものであった。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728395,
      "updated": 1772728413
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b0600000000000edf7e9",
      "text": " \t日本語のローマ字としてCを割り当てるのは合理的だが、従来のKとは異なる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728417,
      "updated": 1772729022
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c7",
      "text": " 子音字の連続によって促音「っ」を表す",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7c8",
      "text": " \t合成語の語源を反映する。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728920
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b2570000000000edf7f9",
      "text": " \tローマ字は、別に日本語の正書法としてかな漢字混じり文の完全劣化互換であるべきではないのである",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728920,
      "updated": 1772728930
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b11f0000000000edf7f2",
      "text": " 長音符号",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728607,
      "updated": 1772728607
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b11f0000000000edf7f3",
      "text": " \t日本語の音節の単位は[モーラ]であり、長音を表記するのに母音字を重ね書きせずにマクロンのみを使用するのは直感的でない。母音字続け字とマクロンを両方採用しても別に構わないだろう",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728607,
      "updated": 1772728607
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b12e0000000000edf7f6",
      "text": " \tマクロンが下に引かれた文字の一つ前の文字の母音の音価で発音する。マクロンが引かれた文字の音価に依らず。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728623,
      "updated": 1772728831
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b1910000000000edf7f8",
      "text": " \t\t例えば、`ax̱`[. （xの下にマクロン）]という綴は「あー」と読む",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728722,
      "updated": 1772728807
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9af210000000000edf7e6",
      "text": "\t全ての符号を上に書くと紛らわしくなるから、重要度の高い長音符号（マクロン）を下に書くのはどうか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728098,
      "updated": 1772728154
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7cb",
      "text": "\tつづら折り",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7cc",
      "text": "\t\ttuduraori",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7cd",
      "text": "\t\ttuẗura-ori",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7ce",
      "text": "\tあっと",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7cf",
      "text": "\t\tatto",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d0",
      "text": "\t\taxto / ax-to",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d1",
      "text": "\t一千万",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d2",
      "text": "\t\tissenman",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d3",
      "text": "\t\titsenman",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d4",
      "text": " 八百",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d5",
      "text": "\t\thappyaku",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d6",
      "text": "\t\thath̊yaku",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d8",
      "text": "試案",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7d9",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/99694ee8aa57f2e7aad66f6fdba04661]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7da",
      "text": "備考",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7db",
      "text": "\t訓令式",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7dc",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/ac206c8ff034b0496c7367c8750311c5]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7dd",
      "text": " ヘボン式 (2026)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7de",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7df",
      "text": " (似非)ヘボン式・英語式",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7e0",
      "text": " \tマクロンを使用しない。長母音の代用表記法が未定義",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9aee00000000000edf7e1",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/8b21c1384153964d770e8bf816bf4638]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772728033,
      "updated": 1772728033
    },
